description: The SPDR MSCI World StrategicFactorsSM ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the MSCI World Factor Mix A-Series Index (the “Index”)Seeks to track a Smart Beta index that blends low volatility, quality and value exposures together in a single strategyThe resulting mix may offer a low-volatility strategy with an equal focus on high-quality and attractively valued firmsMulti-factor smart beta strategies can bridge the gap between active and indexed management, providing an opportunity for investors to rethink exposures and potentially maximize risk-adjusted returns more efficiently
name: SPDR MSCI World StrategicFactors ETF
